Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.27,0:01:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像以前我写的小说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.26,0:01:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平稳的日常生活背后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.34,0:01:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙人和超能力者展开了激烈的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.39,0:01:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们嘲笑这是荒诞无稽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.92,0:01:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.14,0:01:58.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡草卿今天车子被人撞了 还被贴罚单
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.14,0:01:59.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真够惨的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.12,0:02:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别提了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.91,0:02:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖 乖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.24,0:02:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发亮的彩虹？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.84,0:02:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是UFO啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.29,0:02:10.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.22,0:02:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.02,0:02:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们果然是存在的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.61,0:02:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs24}（中奖了）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.10,0:02:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到没 蜜莉娅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.61,0:02:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是日本特产　鬼火啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.14,0:02:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是日本特产 鬼火啊 艾萨克
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.69,0:02:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新 新罗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.83,0:02:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得了了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.83,0:02:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们攻过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.00,0:02:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天 虚构变成了现实
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.87,0:02:52.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord0\fn微软雅黑\1c&Hffffff&}天网{\1c&H0D0EB6&}恢{\1c&HFFFFFF&}恢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.48,0:03:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.19,0:03:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准说阿银的坏话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.06,0:03:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了 冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.84,0:03:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这人竟然说“和那人渣分手”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.72,0:03:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可原谅 快让开
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.04,0:03:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.74,0:03:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只猪算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.79,0:03:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有话到派出所再说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.71,0:03:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再开快点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.69,0:03:23.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.23,0:03:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.02,0:03:33.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是糟糕的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.96,0:03:37.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首都高速路5号池袋线 熊野町交界点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.32,0:03:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生事故 造成8公里长的塞车
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.39,0:03:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是花卷市出身的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.94,0:03:48.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想当美发师 来了东京
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.80,0:03:52.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是一开始连剪刀都不让我拿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.79,0:03:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿银就是那时来找我剃平头认识的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.55,0:04:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那个客人说的对 他这人没出息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.49,0:04:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我过得很苦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.34,0:04:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.71,0:04:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.18,0:04:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是失物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.98,0:04:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我老公的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.65,0:04:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人公是骑摩托的美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.65,0:04:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她持有使用了UFO技术的最终兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.84,0:04:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个组织追逼着她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.81,0:04:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她陷入了穷途末路的危机
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.23,0:05:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,0)}{\fs24}（1小时前）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.96,0:05:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看那边~嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.84,0:05:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.35,0:05:12.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么主人 请戴上这个啵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.55,0:05:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.60,0:05:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可爱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.67,0:05:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝人 很适合你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.02,0:05:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.05,0:05:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面的内容我不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.53,0:05:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们好像说是生食还是人头什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.85,0:05:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这么说的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.42,0:05:48.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人头？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.03,0:05:50.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.48,0:06:11.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏日祭典的三大要素
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.48,0:06:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是苹果棒糖 烟花和浴衣美少女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.61,0:06:16.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就等烟花打上来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.31,0:06:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就是祭典啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.88,0:06:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.60,0:06:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.91,0:06:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.64,0:06:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带着最终兵器逃离组织的博士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.12,0:06:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终被逼到绝境
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.11,0:06:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将其交托给超能力美少女后死去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.97,0:06:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是我写的小说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.82,0:06:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ventra Ventra
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.13,0:06:51.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,space people
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.13,0:06:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外星人 请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.46,0:06:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们念的什么经啊 真是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.67,0:06:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是念经
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.05,0:07:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呼唤UFO的神圣宇宙语
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.47,0:07:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有必要把红包包放在车顶上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.28,0:07:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不这样UFO就不会察觉丢了它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.65,0:07:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天电视上还放过UFO的特别节目呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.37,0:07:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 看了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.04,0:07:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是烂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.97,0:07:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会相信那个的只有你们这些区分不了虚构和现实的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.15,0:07:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是黑摩托
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.07,0:07:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们正在追他 在护国寺附近
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.91,0:07:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 如情报所示 是辆黑摩托
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.83,0:07:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他上哪儿去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.87,0:07:41.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.63,0:07:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.09,0:07:55.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边好像是假的 我马上过去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.88,0:08:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.61,0:08:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开枪了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.63,0:08:25.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是日本吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.18,0:08:27.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是MIB MIB啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.18,0:08:27.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs24}（注：《Men in Black（黑衣人）》）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.96,0:08:30.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是被抓住 会被消除记忆的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.84,0:08:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.93,0:08:36.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全能之神剽窃了我的小说？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.22,0:08:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思考同步？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.04,0:08:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的创作竟然在眼前发生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.89,0:08:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些胡作非为的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.90,0:09:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.50,0:09:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.82,0:09:15.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.28,0:09:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾照
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.04,0:09:46.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情报贩子说得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.32,0:09:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑摩托拿着包
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.15,0:09:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…走私组织？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.44,0:09:56.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快追
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.62,0:10:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“现实比小说更离奇”都是骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.45,0:10:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在现实正在剽窃小说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.00,0:10:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个能取下来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.15,0:10:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.24,0:10:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你取下来了我怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.30,0:10:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这可没法简单去掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.73,0:10:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.94,0:10:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都奇装异服的比较不会害臊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.18,0:10:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是刚才那人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.41,0:10:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人体实验动物化的高中生们也被卷入
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.74,0:10:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,0)}{\fs24}（3小时前）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.20,0:10:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？你说钱被偷了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.31,0:11:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 本来装在交易用的包里放在那里的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.97,0:11:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.15,0:11:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成是粟楠会的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.39,0:11:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来银次郎那小子上哪儿去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.59,0:11:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥说要去医院
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.47,0:11:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像受了重伤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.69,0:11:15.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候在搞什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.56,0:11:17.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先收集情报
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.62,0:11:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联系那个情报贩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.22,0:11:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说被偷了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.31,0:11:25.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来装在交易用的包里放在那里的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.31,0:11:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.59,0:11:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们需要情报 马上联系折原临也
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.39,0:11:44.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正臣说的 今天有祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.02,0:11:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是池袋的风俗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.02,0:11:49.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生穿浴衣参加祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.77,0:11:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都能免费…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.80,0:11:56.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 总之先去阳光大厦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.51,0:12:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定世上多少有一间这样的店呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.00,0:12:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.51,0:12:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼镜美少女穿着强调突出胸部的浴衣不可能不显眼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.13,0:12:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的作战成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.12,0:12:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.42,0:12:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边那位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.42,0:12:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太幸运了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.39,0:12:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.66,0:12:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天带着cosplay美少女的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.46,0:12:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,限一位免费送饮料哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.50,0:12:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 我说得对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.60,0:12:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然跟全员免费差远了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.19,0:12:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三位客人 带路
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.30,0:12:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.21,0:12:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不这么做会被那怪物杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.55,0:12:55.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那家伙的错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.20,0:13:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么那家伙会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.70,0:13:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人啊 一开始也不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.54,0:13:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚认识的时候 他也有追求的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.98,0:13:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.90,0:13:28.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.27,0:13:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想在这个城市出人头地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.11,0:13:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在刚从乡下来的我看来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.93,0:13:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是无比耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.89,0:13:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是个傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.06,0:13:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可他就会装样子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.00,0:13:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱面子买很贵的衣服和手表
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.18,0:13:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了还债去赌博
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.96,0:13:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后越陷越深
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.39,0:13:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托姆兄 我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.30,0:14:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.62,0:14:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会再来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.67,0:14:04.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 手帕我洗了还你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.83,0:14:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.39,0:14:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 差点又要发飙了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.65,0:14:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在受不了这种软弱的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.80,0:14:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,0)}{\fs24}（6小时前）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.31,0:14:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起因是从天而降的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.81,0:14:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸冈先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.18,0:14:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸冈银次郎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.61,0:14:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装不在也是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.63,0:14:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我找你干嘛的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.25,0:14:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 丸冈先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.82,0:14:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿银 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.21,0:14:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我给你做了饭团
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.79,0:14:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.89,0:15:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 再宽限一阵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.15,0:15:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定还钱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.00,0:15:06.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿银
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.78,0:15:10.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小哥你好帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.59,0:15:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像那个演员…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.06,0:15:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽岛幽平 你跟他一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.99,0:15:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你才不像那窝囊废…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.13,0:15:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他踩地雷了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.34,0:15:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才外星人从天上飞过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.93,0:15:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看见了？看见了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.71,0:15:53.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没看见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.50,0:15:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.00,0:16:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那外星人丢的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.40,0:16:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面一定装着毁灭人类的超级武器
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.80,0:16:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能打开 会爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.74,0:16:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不会哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.30,0:16:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外星人要去旅行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.86,0:16:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从天而降的不是美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.43,0:16:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这点跟小说不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.62,0:16:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何 这是我们与它们的第一次接触
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.35,0:16:30.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ventra Ventra
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.00,0:16:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Space people
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.35,0:16:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ventra Ventra
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.04,0:16:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Space people
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.26,0:16:49.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们不知何时已混入我们人类之中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.74,0:16:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻 你身边的人说不定就是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.42,0:16:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.26,0:16:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛啊塞尔堤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.84,0:17:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你突然干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.01,0:17:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 你是真正的新罗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.88,0:17:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.95,0:17:07.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然害怕你还真爱看这种节目啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.09,0:17:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的竟然还录下来看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.65,0:17:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为可怕的对手更需要了解啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.09,0:17:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则万一出事可怎么对付啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.75,0:17:19.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一是什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.11,0:17:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 快递员
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.58,0:17:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.80,0:17:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,临也那家伙 什么叫简单又安全的工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.70,0:17:38.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 Mr.K
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.65,0:17:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们想抢先下手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.94,0:17:43.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么 那是我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.75,0:17:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头儿 看那个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.41,0:17:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.99,0:17:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四木兄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.33,0:18:01.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤脑筋啊 Mr.K
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.87,0:18:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东西说好卖给我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.83,0:18:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.28,0:18:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.50,0:18:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.02,0:18:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想惹麻烦 四木兄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.77,0:18:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还是跟你做交易
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.53,0:18:31.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.66,0:18:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以问问里面是什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.06,0:18:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你一样 是不存在于这世上的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.05,0:18:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有鳞目蜥蜴亚目石龙子科
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.86,0:18:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佛得角巨蜥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.93,0:18:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说70年前便已灭绝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.62,0:18:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过居然还有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.31,0:18:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是专门走私动物的团伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.12,0:18:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种能卖高价呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.85,0:18:59.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过Mr.K背叛了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.48,0:19:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算卖给角筈组
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.65,0:19:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以先发制人 设了个诱他们来这里的局
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.89,0:19:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只是想顺利做个生意而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.48,0:19:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到角筈组都跟来了 多亏了你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.62,0:19:16.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,省了不少事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.50,0:19:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是把生物误读作生食了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.05,0:19:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是现实比小说更离奇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.74,0:19:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了四木兄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.23,0:19:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于角筈组…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.54,0:19:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 不会摧毁他们的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.80,0:19:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定还有用得着他们的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.78,0:19:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 这边怎么用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.28,0:19:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.60,0:19:52.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿回钱了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.66,0:19:54.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太感谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.95,0:19:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有条件？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.35,0:20:03.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一放暑假 又不用上学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.39,0:20:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有意 可以一直不见面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.37,0:20:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以今天才约我们出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.58,0:20:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天后年夏天依然会来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.47,0:20:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过到时候我们不一定会是现在这种关系
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.82,0:20:24.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同样是夏天 还是会有变化啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.84,0:20:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.23,0:20:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天这平平常常的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.48,0:20:30.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和你们一起过个小节
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.28,0:20:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制造点回忆啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.57,0:20:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁是平和岛静雄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.49,0:20:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你吗 偷我们钱的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.04,0:20:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.48,0:20:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我们找回包的情报贩子告诉我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.76,0:20:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是你干的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.83,0:21:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板 行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.17,0:21:03.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.07,0:21:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还真害怕自己的信用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.72,0:21:18.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,UFO啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.72,0:21:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊 帝人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.94,0:21:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.75,0:21:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得不太像…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.36,0:21:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏日祭典的三大要素都齐啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.57,0:21:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微妙…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.77,0:21:36.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,UFO回收了最终兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.63,0:21:38.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城市恢复了和平
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.85,0:21:43.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对日常的背后发生过的激战
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.59,0:21:45.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们一无所知
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.51,0:21:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿银
